template_body:
{% if recipient_role == 'owner' %}
    ‚ûï **Extension Request:** {{ renter_name }} wants to keep the {{ tool_name }} until {{ new_end_date }}.

    **Additional Days:** {{ extra_days }}
    **Your Extra Earnings:** ${{ additional_total_paid * (1 - seller_fee_percent / 100) }}

    Please approve or decline this request in the app.

{% elif recipient_role == 'renter' %}

    ‚è≥ **Extension Pending:** Your request to extend the {{ tool_name }} until {{ new_end_date }} has been sent.

    We will notify you and process the additional payment of ${{ additional_total_paid }} once {{ owner_name }} approves.

{% endif %}

{% if recipient_role == 'renter' %}
    ‚ùå **Booking Cancelled:** The rental for {{ tool_name }} has been cancelled.

    {% if cancelled_by == 'owner' %}
        The owner was unable to fulfill the request. A full refund of ${{ total_paid }} has been processed.
    {% else %}
        Your cancellation is confirmed.
    {% endif %}

{% elif recipient_role == 'owner' %}

    ‚ùå **Booking Cancelled:** The rental for {{ tool_name }} with {{ renter_name }} was cancelled.

    The potential earnings of ${{ total_paid * (1 - seller_fee_percent / 100) }} will not be processed. Your item is now back on the market.

{% endif %}

{% if recipient_role == 'renter' %}
    ‚è∞ Reminder: Your rental for the {{ tool_name }} is due back tomorrow, {{ due_date }}, by {{ due_time }}.

    Please check the owner's return instructions to ensure a smooth drop-off: {{ return_instructions_link }}.

{% elif recipient_role == 'owner' %}

    üóìÔ∏è Heads up! Your {{ tool_name }} (Rented by {{ renter_name }}) is scheduled to be returned tomorrow, {{ due_date }}, by {{ due_time }}.

    Please ensure your drop-off location is accessible for the renter.

{% endif %}

{% if recipient_role == 'renter' %}
    üì¢ **DUE TODAY:** Your rental for the {{ tool_name }} must be returned today by {{ due_time }} to avoid late fees.

    Coordinate with the owner via chat if you have any issues!

{% elif recipient_role == 'owner' %}

    ‚úÖ **DUE TODAY:** Your {{ tool_name }} (Rented by {{ renter_name }}) is scheduled to be returned today by {{ due_time }}.

    Please prepare to receive the tool and mark the rental as complete upon drop-off.

{% endif %}

{% if recipient_role == 'owner' %}
üì¢ New Inquiry: {{ tool_name }}

{{ renter_name }} has started a conversation about your **{{ tool_name }}**.

They are interested in the period from **{{ start_date }} to {{ end_date }}**, with an estimated cost of **${{ total_cost }}**.

Please respond to {{ renter_name }} in this chat to coordinate details and confirm availability.
{% endif %}

{% if recipient_role == 'renter' %}
‚úÖ Conversation Started!

Your message thread for the **{{ tool_name }}** has been successfully created. The owner, {{ owner_name }}, has been notified of your interest.

You can now use this chat to coordinate dates and pickup details directly with the owner.
{% endif %}

{% if recipient_role == 'renter' %}
    üö® Your rental for the {{ tool_name }} is OVERDUE! It was due back at {{ due_time }} on {{ due_date }}.

    Late fees of {{ late_fee_amount }} per day are now applying. Please contact {{ owner_name }} immediately to arrange the return.

{% elif recipient_role == 'owner' %}

    ‚ö†Ô∏è The rental for your {{ tool_name }} (Rented by {{ renter_name }}) is now overdue. 

    The system has started applying late fees. You may contact the renter now to follow up.

{% endif %}

{% if recipient_role == 'renter' %}
    üéâ Rental Confirmed! Your booking for the {{ tool_name }} from {{ owner_name }} is confirmed for {{ start_date }} to {{ end_date }}.

    Pickup location: {{ location_address }}. Total Paid: ${{ total_paid }}.

{% elif recipient_role == 'owner' %}

    ‚úÖ New Booking Confirmed! The {{ tool_name }} has been rented by {{ renter_name }} for the period {{ start_date }} to {{ end_date }}.

    Please prepare the tool for pickup at {{ pickup_time }}. 
    **Total Earnings:** ${{ total_paid * (1 - seller_fee_percent / 100) }}.

{% endif %}

{% if recipient_role == 'owner' %}
    üîî **Action Required:** New Rental Request for {{ tool_name }}!

    {{ renter_name }} has requested to rent your tool from {{ start_date }} to {{ end_date }}.

    **Total Price:** ${{ total_paid }}
    **Your Potential Earnings:** ${{ total_paid * (1 - seller_fee_percent / 100) }}

    Please accept or decline this request within 24 hours.

{% elif recipient_role == 'renter' %}

    ‚è≥ Request Sent! 

    We have sent your request for the {{ tool_name }} to {{ owner_name }}.

    Your card will only be charged once the owner accepts the booking. We will notify you as soon as they respond!

{% endif %}
